{"tid":1783744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賤賊只顧執行政治任務，唔盡返原有嘅責任","createTime":"2019-12-15T06:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T10:55:32.000Z","uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5264962792e0962d19a306ed60f51ec81edbcde","tid":1783744,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497734-20191215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497734-20191215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=8db3f4cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497734-20191215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=db3ebc14\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497734-20191215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">觀塘爆竊案保安員遇襲延至昨日不治 賤方改列謀殺案</span></span><br />\n觀塘一間食肆星期三凌晨被爆竊，一名65歲保安員遇襲受傷，延至昨日早上死亡。賤方將案改列作謀殺及嚴重入屋犯法罪案處理，由東九龍總區重案組調查。<br />\n<br />\n被爆竊的食肆損失約5萬元現金，保安員遇襲後頭部受傷昏迷，倒臥於觀塘開源道一幢大廈之梯間，賤方稍後將安排驗屍以確定死因。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">保護市民嘅先係真警察<br />\n草菅市民人命係叫<span style=\"color: red;\">賤賊</span></span></span><br />\n你班垃圾賤官永遠都將政治任務放第一位<br />\n睇吓而家香港搞成點撚樣?<br />\n選擇性執法導致香港更加亂已經係大罪<br />\n仲夠膽死講止暴制亂?越止越暴，越制越亂，屌你老母臭閪<br />\n含撚奴隸聰就由內到外都戇鳩鳩咁<br />\n鄧小強你個樣一睇就知唔係咁撚戇鳩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該用捉示威者嘅頭腦，去諗點樣減少人命傷亡<br />\n咪撚再殘害香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"1144a4ab6c07fdf7f345da5911990184c5fc53b8","tid":1783744,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"佢地依幾個月都搵夠仲捉賊黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe662b642c6b0d9cb820167134c4f2c84dbc493","tid":1783744,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxw98m6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwxw98m6.jpg&h=acb4e193&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2125e4d63be7fd220826332dac5ac8af00001e85","tid":1783744,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe662b642c6b0d9cb820167134c4f2c84dbc493","tid":1783744,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxw98m6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwxw98m6.jpg&h=acb4e193&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eHJtnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eHJtnf.jpg&h=6a79841a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8005074062bac2397278730fb670b1f4e10cc842","tid":1783744,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"捉賊即係捉小強兄弟，無得升。捉政治犯有得升。呢班已經變成黨衛軍。"},{"pid":"89d6df97fd5955c778b1482cbc581cef44dc0ad5","tid":1783744,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"208a4cc3cc676b2d1b97c54975b864e6b97ed0fd","tid":1783744,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8005074062bac2397278730fb670b1f4e10cc842","tid":1783744,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"捉賊即係捉小強兄弟，無得升。捉政治犯有得升。呢班已經變成黨衛軍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁又係<br />\n而家呢班係賤賊呀嗎<br />\n賤賊自己都係賊，又點會捉自己兄弟?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}